{"updated_at": {"date": {"d": "03", "m": "06", "Y": "2026"}, "time": {"H": "02", "M": "38", "S": "08"}}, "news": [{"title": "Jhansi greenfield industrial city gets environment clearance", "para": "The Union Ministry of Environment, Forest and Climate Change has granted environmental clearance to the Bundelkhand Industrial Development Authority\u2019s greenfield industrial city project in Jhansi. The project, planned across 62,599.20 acres, is expected to attract investment of about \u20b91.51 lakh crore and generate employment for over 5.6 lakh people.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/industry/jhansi-greenfield-industrial-city-receives-environmental-clearance-with-151-lakh-crore-investment/131467279?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-2238554/131467279.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "industry"}, {"title": "Adani Properties highest bidder for MHADA\u2019s Worli, Bandra redevelopment projects", "para": "Adani Properties has emerged as the highest bidder for MHADA\u2019s cluster redevelopment projects at Adarsh Nagar in Worli and Bandra Reclamation, while a consortium comprising Hanura Realty, Chandak Realtors, Premsagar Infra Realty and Vantier Realty has emerged as the highest bidder for the S.V.P. Nagar project in Andheri West.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/industry/adani-properties-wins-major-bids-for-mumbais-redevelopment-projects/131465387?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-71380/131465387.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "industry"}, {"title": "Welspun One plans to lease over 10 million sq ft in next three years", "para": "Welspun One plans to lease over 10 million sq ft of warehousing and industrial real estate in the next three years, nearly doubling its current operational footprint. The company is expan